aVPresident Donald Trump on Thursday said he did not believe that Iran was living up to the spirit of the 2015 deal to curtail its nuclear weapons program.\u000a\u000a"I don't think Iran is in compliance," Trump told reporters at his private New Jersey golf club. "I don't they're living up to the spirit of the agreement."
