ational \u2014 Locations in the U.S., Canada, and the Caribbean offer 10 percent or more savings to AARP members. Members also earn 10-percent bonus points when joining the Best Western Rewards program, according to HotelPlanner.\u000a\u000a\u200b7. Hilton Hotels & Resorts \u2014 AARP members receive up to 10 percent off the best available rate along with breakfast for families. Families of members may get 5 percent off the stay.\u000a\u000a8. Starwood Hotels & Resorts \u2014 The hotels and resorts offer between 5 and 15 percent off the best available rates for AARP members.\u000a\u000aIMPORTANT: Heart Surgeon's Secret to Healthy Blood Pressure
